    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and kept in tip-top shape, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
