      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by a pristine, smoke-free interior that retains its original factory luster. Mechanically impeccable and rigorously inspected, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle in peerless condition. Every detail, from the precision of the powertrain to the integrity of the cabin materials, reflects a legacy of uncompromising care.",
