      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and treated with so much love. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014totally flawless and smells like new! I'm only selling because I'm downsizing, but I'd love for it to go to a great home where it'll be appreciated. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
