    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform, maintained to a standard that exceeds factory requirements. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 features individual throttle bodies and delivers a linear power curve up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement with treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators, has been documented to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The chassis retains its original rigidity, with no bushing deflection or subframe fatigue. The M-Variable Differential Lock and EDC dampers function flawlessly, providing a communicative and sharp handling profile. The exterior finish displays exceptional depth with zero clear coat failure, while the interior leather maintains its original matte texture. This is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
